plans.name: Monthly
plans.description: The Monthly plus plan includes 90 minutes of rental time each calendar day for 30 days. Additional minutes are charged at the Pay As You Go. All other fees and credits are described in the Rental Policy. Thank you for riding Breeze.

plans.name: Pay-As-You-Go
plans.description:
Pay-As-You-Go plan requires a minimum purchase of $7 to initiate a prepaid balance on the account. 

Please note, when registering for this plan, your password must be at least 7 characters and include one Capital letter and 1 number. Entering a Metro TAP card number is optional.

Thank you for choosing to ride Breeze!
